import React from 'react'
import Header from './Header'
import Navbar from './Navbar'
import Footer from './Footer'
import SearchShimmer from './SearchShimmer'
const Search = () => {

  return (
    <>
    <Header/>
    <Navbar/>
    <SearchShimmer/>
    <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Search
